burn(address,uint256).notice: Burns LP tokens from the given address.

mint(address,uint256).notice: Mints new LP tokens to the given address.

userdoc.notice: LP token which is minted and burned by the Pair contract to represent liquidity in the pool.

params.baseTokenAmount: The amount of base tokens to add.
params.deadline: The deadline before the trade expires.
params.fractionalTokenAmount: The amount of fractional tokens to add.
params.maxPrice: The maximum price that the pool should currently be at.
params.minLpTokenAmount: The minimum amount of LP tokens to mint.
params.minPrice: The minimum price that the pool should currently be at.

returns.lpTokenAmount: The amount of LP tokens minted.

addQuote(uint256,uint256,uint256).details: Calculated as a share of existing deposits. If there are no existing deposits, then initializes to      sqrt(baseTokenAmount * fractionalTokenAmount).

params.baseTokenAmount: The amount of base tokens to add.
params.fractionalTokenAmount: The amount of fractional tokens to add.

returns._0: lpTokenAmount The amount of lp tokens received.

params.deadline: The deadline before the trade expires.
params.maxInputAmount: The maximum amount of base tokens to spend.
params.outputAmount: The amount of fractional tokens to buy.

returns.inputAmount: The amount of base tokens spent.

buyQuote(uint256).details: Calculated using the xyk invariant and a 30bps fee.

params.outputAmount: The amount of fractional tokens to buy.

returns._0: inputAmount The amount of base tokens required.

close().details: Can only be called by the caviar owner. This is used as an emergency exit in case      the caviar owner suspects that the pair has been compromised.

params.baseTokenAmount: The amount of base tokens to add.
params.maxPrice: The maximum price of the pair.
params.minLpTokenAmount: The minimum amount of lp tokens to receive.
params.minPrice: The minimum price of the pair.
params.proofs: The merkle proofs for the NFTs.
params.tokenIds: The ids of the NFTs to add.

returns.lpTokenAmount: The amount of lp tokens minted.

params.deadline: The deadline before the trade expires.
params.maxInputAmount: The maximum amount of base tokens to spend.
params.tokenIds: The ids of the NFTs to buy.

returns.inputAmount: The amount of base tokens spent.

params.deadline: The deadline before the trade expires.
params.lpTokenAmount: The amount of lp tokens to remove.
params.minBaseTokenOutputAmount: The minimum amount of base tokens to receive.
params.tokenIds: The ids of the NFTs to remove.
params.withFee: Whether to pay a fee for unwrapping or not.

returns.baseTokenOutputAmount: The amount of base tokens received.
returns.fractionalTokenOutputAmount: The amount of fractional tokens received.

params.deadline: The deadline before the trade expires.
params.minOutputAmount: The minimum amount of base tokens to receive.
params.proofs: The merkle proofs for the NFTs.
params.tokenIds: The ids of the NFTs to sell.

returns.outputAmount: The amount of base tokens received.

price().details: Calculated by dividing the base token reserves by the fractional token reserves.

returns._0: price The price of one fractional token in base tokens * 1e18.

params.deadline: The deadline before the trade expires.
params.lpTokenAmount: The amount of LP tokens to burn.
params.minBaseTokenOutputAmount: The minimum amount of base tokens to receive.
params.minFractionalTokenOutputAmount: The minimum amount of fractional tokens to receive.

returns.baseTokenOutputAmount: The amount of base tokens received.
returns.fractionalTokenOutputAmount: The amount of fractional tokens received.

removeQuote(uint256).details: Calculated as a share of existing deposits.

params.lpTokenAmount: The amount of lp tokens to burn.

returns._0: baseTokenAmount The amount of base tokens received.
returns._1: fractionalTokenAmount The amount of fractional tokens received.

params.deadline: The deadline before the trade expires.
params.inputAmount: The amount of fractional tokens to sell.
params.minOutputAmount: The minimum amount of base tokens to receive.

returns.outputAmount: The amount of base tokens received.

sellQuote(uint256).details: Calculated using the xyk invariant and a 30bps fee.

params.inputAmount: The amount of fractional tokens to sell.

returns._0: outputAmount The amount of base tokens received.

params.tokenIds: The ids of the NFTs to unwrap.
params.withFee: Whether to pay a fee for unwrapping or not.

returns.fractionalTokenAmount: The amount of fractional tokens burned.

withdraw(uint256).details: Can only be called by the caviar owner after the close grace period has passed. This      is used to auction off the NFTs in the pair in case NFTs get stuck due to liquidity      imbalances. Proceeds from the auction should be distributed pro rata to fractional      token holders. See documentation for more details.

params.proofs: The merkle proofs for the NFTs proving that they can be used in the pair.
params.tokenIds: The ids of the NFTs to wrap.

returns.fractionalTokenAmount: The amount of fractional tokens minted.

addQuote(uint256,uint256,uint256).notice: The amount of lp tokens received for adding a given amount of base tokens and fractional tokens.

buy(uint256,uint256,uint256).notice: Buys fractional tokens from the pair.

buyQuote(uint256).notice: The amount of base tokens required to buy a given amount of fractional tokens.

close().notice: Closes the pair to new wraps.

nftAdd(uint256,uint256[],uint256,uint256.notice: nftAdd Adds liquidity to the pair using NFTs.

nftBuy(uint256[],uint256,uint256).notice: Buys NFTs from the pair using base tokens.

nftRemove(uint256,uint256,uint256,uint25.notice: Removes liquidity from the pair using NFTs.

nftSell(uint256[],uint256,uint256,bytes3.notice: Sells NFTs to the pair for base tokens.

price().notice: The current price of one fractional token in base tokens with 18 decimals of precision.

removeQuote(uint256).notice: The amount of base tokens and fractional tokens received for burning a given amount of lp tokens.

sell(uint256,uint256,uint256).notice: Sells fractional tokens to the pair.

sellQuote(uint256).notice: The amount of base tokens received for selling a given amount of fractional tokens.

withdraw(uint256).notice: Withdraws a particular NFT from the pair.

userdoc.notice: A pair of an NFT and a base token that can be used to create and trade fractionalized NFTs.

params.messages: The messages signed by the reservoir oracle.
params.tokenAddress: The address of the NFT contract.
